      </p>

      <h3>2. Cancellations</h3>
      <p>
        Monthly subscriptions may be cancelled at any time and will remain active until the
        end of the current paid period. No further payments will be taken after cancellation.
      </p>

      <h3>3. Failed Payments</h3>
      <p>
        If a payment fails, your account will automatically revert to the
        <em>Free</em> tier until the issue is resolved.
        Once payment is successfully processed, access to your original tier will be restored immediately.
      </p>

